Constructor Detail

HGoodMinus

public HGoodMinus(double[][] mappingScores,
                  double threshHold)
Constructor that populates the good and Minus HashMaps which together represent the H list in the algorithm. The key-set for both the maps need to be same at every point

Parameters:
mappingScores - Matrix that stores matching scores for every pair of vertices in the graph v - v'
threshHold - The threshold value, matches below which go into minus list and rest in the good list
